# 🏥 Healthcare Management System

A complete **Healthcare Management System** built using **Spring Boot** and **MySQL**.  
This project helps manage **patients, doctors, appointments, medical records, billing, and reports** efficiently.  

---

## 🚀 Features

✅ Patient Management (Add, View, Update, Delete)  
✅ Doctor Management  
✅ Appointment Booking System  
✅ Medical Records Tracking  
✅ Billing System  
✅ Admin Panel  
✅ Reports Export  

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- **Backend:** Spring Boot, Java  
- **Database:** MySQL  
- **Tools:** Maven, Postman (for testing APIs)  
- **Version Control:** Git, GitHub  

